description: Defines the Note class representing a note entity with serialization and deserialization methods for interacting with a database or API.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Represents a note with fields for id, title, content, creation, and update timestamps, including methods for converting to and from Map for data exchange.

methods.name: Note.fromMap
methods.description: Factory constructor that creates a Note instance from a Map, parsing data types accordingly.

methods.name: Note.toMap
methods.description: Converts a Note instance into a Map<String, dynamic>, optionally including the id.
